---
// Packages section for the landing page
---
<section id='packages' class='py-20 px-4 bg-brand-dark'>
  <div class='max-w-6xl mx-auto'>
    <div class='text-center mb-12'>
      <h2 class='text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text-light'>Paquetes de Publicidad</h2>
      <p class='text-text-muted mt-2'>Soluciones directas para un impacto real.</p>
    </div>
    <div class='grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center'>
      <div class='bg-brand-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-brand-card/50 h-full flex flex-col'>
        <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold text-text-light mb-2'>STARTER</h3>
        <p class='text-text-muted mb-6 flex-grow'>Ideal para estudios indie y marcas emergentes.</p>
        <p class='text-4xl font-black text-text-light mb-6'>$175</p>
        <ul class='text-text-muted space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow'>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 5 streamers</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 1 hora de transmisión</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 30-70 viewers simultáneos</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> Alcance: 150 - 350 únicos</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> Story en red social</li>
        </ul>
        <a href='#' class='w-full text-center bg-brand-purple/20 text-text-light font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-purple/40 transition-colors mt-auto'>Elegir Plan</a>
      </div>
      <div class='bg-brand-card p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-brand-pink shadow-[0_0_20px_0_rgba(255,45,146,0.3)] relative flex flex-col'>
        <span class='absolute top-0 -translate-y-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-brand-pink text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase'>Más Popular</span>
        <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold text-text-light mb-2'>PRO</h3>
        <p class='text-text-muted mb-6 flex-grow'>Para campañas de visibilidad media.</p>
        <p class='text-5xl font-black text-text-light mb-6'>$320</p>
        <ul class='text-text-muted space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow'>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 10 streamers</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 1 hora de transmisión</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 30-70 viewers simultáneos</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> Alcance: 300 - 700 únicos</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> Story en red social</li>
        </ul>
        <a href='#' class='w-full text-center bg-brand-pink text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity mt-auto'>Elegir Plan</a>
      </div>
      <div class='bg-brand-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-brand-card/50 h-full flex flex-col'>
        <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold text-text-light mb-2'>ELITE</h3>
        <p class='text-text-muted mb-6 flex-grow'>Para grandes lanzamientos y alto impacto.</p>
        <p class='text-4xl font-black text-text-light mb-6'>$599</p>
        <ul class='text-text-muted space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow'>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 20 streamers</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 1 hora de transmisión</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> 30-70 viewers simultáneos</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> Alcance: 600 - 1400 únicos</li>
          <li class='flex items-center'><span class='text-brand-pink mr-3'>✓</span> Story en red social</li>
        </ul>
        <a href='#' class='w-full text-center bg-brand-purple/20 text-text-light font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-purple/40 transition-colors mt-auto'>Elegir Plan</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
